Read LINX Links File

Source: R/linx_tab.R
linx_links_read.Rd

Reads the linx.links.tsv file.

Usage

linx_links_read(x)

Arguments

x

Path to linx.links.tsv file.

Value

The input file as a tibble.

Examples

x <- system.file("extdata/tables/COLO829v003T.linx.links.tsv", package = "linxreport")
(l <- linx_links_read(x))
